features: Constructed of lightweight and durable DuraTec fabric that stands up to rigors of travel and looks great; hanging, removable bi-fold organizer included
Dual Density, double-spinner wheels assure a stable base with multi-directional rolling with zero weight on your hand for easy travel; expands up to 2" for additional packing space
Spacious interior offers 2 shoe pockets, a mesh pocket, and a wet pocket for maximum organization; 2 exterior pockets for easy access to essentials
Recessed 3-dial TSA approved combination lock for security; features patented SECURITECH zip, a closing system that is 3 times more resistant to intrusion than a conventional zipper
Ergonomical handle for maneuverability with soft-grip side, top and bottom carrying handles; backed by a manufacturer’s 10-year limited warranty
body.description: Established in 1946, Delsey has used its flair to marry tradition with innovation, elegance with modernity and design with practicality. We design tomorrow's luggage with inspiration from many places: travelers and their journeys, societal changes and the evolving environment. As a result our luggage keeps getting lighter, better fitted and more environmentally friendly. Enabling our customers to travel elegantly and limiting any negative impact on the environment is our raison d’être.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Attractive and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: I've used this bag on several trips now and am very glad I purchased it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So light weight
reviews.reviewText: Light weight, very well thought out piece of luggage, very roomy lots of storage and liner unzips to be washed. Plus, locks that TCA can open if necessary. Has pockets for a pair if shoes and so much more. Almost forgot wheels on luggage move effortlessly. Best suitcase ever purchased.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I couldnt be more pleased with this suitcase. The color is great and easy to find luggage in the sea of black and gray suitcases but its lightweight and easy to maneuver. The storage space is perfectly designed and size is spot on. I used this for my 3wk trip along with a smaller carry on and everything fit perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Flimsy handle, stopped working after two uses
reviews.reviewText: Appreciate the light weight feel and it glides fairly smoothly, but frustratingly the handle stopped working after just two light uses. Handle immediately was temperamental, taking a few different tries to lock into the right level and just two trips later could not extend fully. Would not recommend buying, there are better, more reliable brands out there for a similar price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great bag. High quality.
reviews.reviewText: This is a large bag. The zippers are of a high quality, as are the wheels. This purchase was worth the money

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I am very satisfied with the purchase of this luggage. Very well constructed. Zippers are sturdy and glide easily. Wheels and mounting hardware sturdy. Material used to encase appears it can take a lot of punishment and not tear or develop holes easily. And the bilirubin in combination lock is a plus. Great purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Glides through the airport
reviews.reviewText: I like that this suitcase just glides along while you drag, shove or pull it. Just got back from a trip to Europe and used it. It has some neat compartments inside to stow things like shoes, toiletries, etc. Also has an expandable zipper to help cram more stuff inside. I would have given it 5 stars but the zipper is a little tough to open or close if the suitcase is full.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars THE BEST-⭐️ A MUST BUY ⭐️
reviews.reviewText: DELSEY has always been my go to for luggage, it never fails. I just had to replace my old Delsey, I think it lasted over 15 years. I immediately purchased a new one, and couldn’t be happier. Sturdy, ROOMY, and just so reliable. I absolutely love Delsey, especially the bigger sized luggage. ⭐️ A MUST BUY ⭐️
Justo lo que necesito de un carry on, tal cual aparece en la foto llego elDía señalado … eso me gusta !

I wanted mid size travel luggage for my European holiday. This bag worked very well. It traveled through all the airports and busses with no major mishaps, tears, rips or damage.The only thing that became an issue was the pull-up handle ..... it seems to jam in one spot and becomes almost impossible to budge. It does work and does not appear to be damaged so unsure what would cause this jamming situation?I think I will get lots of use with this bag with my next adventures. I am a DELSEY luggage fan, this is my third case and give it a thumbs up.

reviews.reviewTitle: Las maletas tamaño carry on están muy bonitas
reviews.reviewText: Hice el ejercicio de meter ropa para 10 días de viaje y sin zapatos muy voluminosos ( que puedo llevar puestos) y cupo todo perfecto! , es espaciosa, buenos a acabados y se desliza de maravilla. Solo me queda una duda, si de verdad no habrá problema en ninguna línea aérea para subirla a cabina, pues no mide los 55 cm reglamentarios, con las ruedas mide 60 cm. Hice la pregunta para ver si alguna persona ya viajo con ella en cabina sin problemas, ojalá me respondan positivamente, no me gustaría devolverla.
